@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.42 + v1 + 0.26) / (v0 + 0.57 + v2 + 0.30)))
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.61 + tmp + 0.40) * 0.81) + tmp)
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = (v2 + tmp)
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.cos((v2 + 0.73 * tmp + 0.22)))
    v2 = (tmp / (wp.abs(v2 + 0.86) - tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
